{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;Cat Island Petrichor&quot;</strong> is an exploration adventure game where players take on the role of a cat and solve mysteries set on a beautiful cat island in Japan.<br><strong>Welcome to the summer cat island!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/A.jpg?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In order to create a report, a young girl named Makoto visits a certain cat island to unravel the &quot;mysteries hidden on the island.&quot;<br>She begins her full-scale investigation in preparation for the &quot;island festival&quot; that will take place in seven days.<br>Explore facilities such as the once prosperous lighthouse, shrine, and museum, and uncover the hidden mysteries of the island.<br><strong>You are a cat!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/B.jpg?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/C.jpg?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will become a white cat living on the cat island and assist Makoto in her investigation of the &quot;mysteries hidden on the island.&quot;<br>Using cat-specific controls, you will help solve various puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The investigation begins! The story of a white cat and a girl.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/D.png?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/E.jpg?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/F.png?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The story unfolds as you follow Makoto in pursuit of the &quot;hidden mysteries&quot; on the cat island.<br>While delving into the heart of the story, you can freely explore the island, enjoy small puzzles, and interact with the island's residents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The island's colorful residents</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/G.jpg?t=1736412394\" /><br>Many unique residents live on the cat island.<br>A mother and child running a diner, a shrine maiden, a receptionist at the tourist information center, and other heroines with distinct personalities will assist with the investigation.<br>Additionally, there are scenarios depicting interactions with each heroine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/H.png?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/I.png?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/J.png?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/J.png?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/K.png?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/L.png?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Heroines' vulnerable moments in front of the cat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/M.jpg?t=1736412394\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/N.jpg?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While enjoying interactions with the heroines, you can catch glimpses of their vulnerable sides, such as bathing scenes or moments of unguarded charm.<br>Furthermore, progressing with the heroines' scenarios will allow you to obtain more captivating stills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Choices between the cat and the girl</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/O.png?t=1736412394\" /><br>The ending of the story is branchable! What exactly are the mysteries of the cat island?<br>The boundary between humans and cats begins to blur...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game Volume</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">5 areas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">5 heroines</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1 or more scenarios per heroine</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">214+ event scenes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">150,000+ total text</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">265+ total voice recording minutes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spine animations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">10 facial expression variations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">5 pose/costume variations (main characters)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">24 CGs, 60 including variations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">30+ puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">10+ items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Playtime: 6 to 12 hours</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Available languages: Japanese, English, Traditional Chinese, Simplified Chinese, Korean, Spanish</p></li></ul>","background":"https: