hite cat living on the cat island and assist Makoto in her investigation of the &quot;mysteries hidden on the island.&quot;<br>Using cat-specific controls, you will help solve various puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The investigation begins! The story of a white cat and a girl.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/D.png?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/E.jpg?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/F.png?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The story unfolds as you follow Makoto in pursuit of the &quot;hidden mysteries&quot; on the cat island.<br>While delving into the heart of the story, you can freely explore the island, enjoy small puzzles, and interact with the island's residents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The island's colorful residents</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/G.jpg?t=1736412394\" /><br>Many unique residents live on the cat island.<br>A mother and child running a diner, a shrine maiden, a receptionist at the tourist information center, and other heroines with distinct personalities will assist with the investigation.<br>Additionally, there are scenarios depicting interactions with each heroine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/H.png?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181890/extras/I.png?t=1736412394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_im